quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  19,59,"fata min baed hwla' almneam ealayhim 'atbae saw' tarakuu alsalat klha, 'aw fwtu wqtha, 'aw tarakuu arkanha wwajbatha, watabaeuu ma ywafq shhwathm wylaymha, fasawf yalqawn shrana wdlala wakhaybat fi jhnm"
  19,60,"lkn man tab minhum min dhanbih waman birabih waeamil salhana tsdyqana ltwbth, fawlyk yaqbal allah twbthm, wydkhlwn aljanat mae almuminin wala yunqaswn shyyana min 'aemalahum alsalht"
  19,61,"jnat khld wa'iiqamat daymt, wahi alati wueid alrhmn biha eibadah bialghayb famanu biha walam yrwha, 'iina waed allah lieibadih bhdhh aljanat at la mhalt"
  19,62,"la yasmae 'ahl aljanat fiha klamana batilana lkn yasmaeun salamana tahiatan lhm, walahum rizquhum fiha min altaeam walshrab daymana, kulama shawu bukratan weshyana"
  19,63,"tlk aljanat almwswft bitilk alsfat, hi alty nwrthha wnetyha eibadina almutaqin lna, bamtthal awamrna wajtnab nwahyna"
  19,64,"waqul - ya jbryl - lmhmd: wama natanazal - nahn almalayikat - min alsama' 'iilaa al'ard 'iilaa bi'amr rabik lna, lah ma bayn 'aydina mimaa yastaqbil min 'amr alakhrt, wama khalfana mimaa madaa min aldnya, wama bayn aldunya walakhrt, falah al'amr kuluh fi alzman walmkan, wama kan rabuk nasyana lishay' min alashya'"
  19,65,"fhw allah rabu alsmwat wal'ard wama bynhma, wmalk dhlk klh wkhalqh wmdbrh, faebudh wahdah - 'ayuha alnabiu - wasbir ealaa taeth 'ant wman tbek, lays kamithlih shay' fi dhatih wasmayh wsfath wafealh"
  19,66,"wyqwl al'iinsan alkafir mnkrana llbeth baed almwt: 'a'iidha ma mitt wfanit lasawf 'ukhraj min qbry hyana?"
  19,67,"kyf nasi hdha al'iinsan alkafir nfsh? 'awala yadhkur 'anaa khalaqnah 'awal mrt, walam yk shyyana mwjwdana?"
  19,68,"fwrbk - 'ayuha alrasul - lnjmen hwla' almnkryn llbeth yawm alqiamat mae alshyatyn, thuma lnatyn bihim 'ajmaein hawl jahanam barkyn ealaa rukabhm; lshdt maa hum fih min alhwl, laa yaqdirun ealaa alqyam"
  19,69,"thm lnakhdhnn min kuli tayifat ashddahm tmrdana wesyanana llh, fnbda bedhabhm"
  19,70,thm lanahn 'aelam bialadhin hum 'awla bidukhul alnaar wmqasat hrha
  19,71,"wma minkum - 'ayuha alnaas - 'ahad 'iilaa warid alnaar balmrwr ealaa alsirat almnswb ealaa matn jhnm, kl bhsb emlh, kan dhlk amrana mhtwmana, qadaa allah - subhanah - wahukim 'anah la bd min wuqueih la mhalt"
  19,72,"thm nunajiy aladhin ataqawa rabahum btaeth walbed ean mesyth, wntrk alzaalimin lanfshm bialkufr biallah fi alnaar barkyn ealaa rukabhm"
  19,73,"w'idha ttla ealaa alnaas ayatina almnzlat alwadhat qal alkufaar biallah lilmuminin bh: ay alfariqayn mnna waminkum 'afdal munzalana wa'ahsan mjlsana?"
  19,74,wkthyrana 'ahlakna qabl kafaar qawmak - 'ayuha alrasul - min al'umam kanuu 'ahsan mtaeana minhum wajml mnzrana
  19,75,"qul - 'ayuha alrasul - lhm: man kan dalana ean alhaqu ghyr mtbe tariq alhda, fallah ymhlh wymly lah fi dlalh, hataa 'iidha ra'aa - yaqinana - ma tweeadh allah bh: 'iimaa aleadhab aleajil fi aldnya, wa'iimaa qiam alsaet, fsyelm - hinayidh - man hu sharun mkanana wmstqrana, wa'adeaf quatan wjndana"
  19,76,"wyzyd allah eibadah aladhin ahtadawa ldynh hudana ealaa hudahum bima yatajadad lahum min al'iiman bfrayd allh, waleamal bha. walaemal albaqyat alsaalihat khayr thwabana eind allah fi alakhrt, wakhayr mrjeana weaqbt"
  19,77,"aealimt - 'ayuha alrasul - wejbt mn hdha alkafir \"aleas bin wayl\" wamthalh? 'iidh kafar biayat allah wkdhdhab biha wqal: laetynn fi alakhirat 'amwalana wawladana"
  19,78,"attalae alghyb, fraa 'ana lah malana wwldana, 'am lah eind allah eahid bdhlk?"
  19,79,"lys al'amr kama yazeum dhlk alkafr, fala eilm lah wala eahid endh, sanaktub ma yaqul min kadhab waftra' ealaa allh, wnzydh fi alakhirat min 'anwae aleqwbat, kama aizdad min alghy waldlal"
  19,80,"wnrthh malah wwldh, wayatina yawm alqiamat frdana whdh, la mal maeah wala wld"
  19,81,"watkhdh almushrikun alihatan yebdwnha min dun allh; ltnsrhm, wyetzu bha"
  19,82,"lys al'amr kama yzemwn, ln takun lahum alalihat ezana, bal stkfr hadhih alalihat fi alakhirat bieibadatihim lha, watakun ealayhim aewanana fi khswmthm wtkdhybhm bkhlaf ma znwh fyha"
  19,83,"alm tar - 'ayuha alrasul - anna sllatna alshayatin ealaa alkafirin biallah wrslh; ltghwyhm, wtdfehm ean alttaeat 'iilaa almesy?"
  19,84,"fla tastaejil - 'ayuha alrasul - bitalab aleadhab ealaa hwla' alkafryn, 'iinama nhsy 'aemaruhum waemalhm 'ihsa'an la tfryt fih wala takhyr"
  19,85,ywm najmae almutaqin 'iilaa rabihim alrahim bihim wfwdana mkrmyn. wanasuq alkafirin biallah swqana shdydana 'iilaa alnaar mushat eitashana
  19,86,yawm najmae almutaqin 'iilaa rabihim alrahim bihim wfwdana mkrmyn. wanasuq alkafirin biallah swqana shdydana 'iilaa alnaar mushat eitashana
  19,87,"la yamlik hwla' alkufaar alshafaeat lahd, 'iinama yamlikuha man atakhadh eind alrhmn ehdana bdhlk, wahum almuminun biallah wrslh"
  19,88,"wqal hwla' alkfar: atakhadh alrhmn wldana"
  19,89,lqd jitum - 'ayuha alqaylwn - bhdhh almqalt shayyana ezymana mnkrana
  19,90,"tkad alsmwat ytshqqaqn min fzaet dhlkm alqwl, wttsde alard, watusqit aljibal sqwtana shdydana ghdbana lilah linisbatihm lah alwld. taealaa allah ean dhlk elwana kbyrana"
  19,91,"tkad alsmwat ytshqqaqn min fzaet dhlkm alqwl, wttsde alard, watusqit aljibal sqwtana shdydana ghdbana lilah linisbatihm lah alwld. taealaa allah ean dhlk elwana kbyrana"
  19,92,"wma yuslih llrhmn, wala ylyq bezmth, 'an yatakhidh wldana; li'ana aitikhadh alwld yadulu ealaa alnaqs walhajt, wallah hu alghaniu alhamid almbra ean kl alnqays"
  19,93,"ma kl man fi alsmwat min almlaykt, wman fi al'ard min al'iins waljn, 'iilaa syaty rabih yawm alqiamat ebdana dhlyla khadeana mqrana lah balebwdyt"
  19,94,"lqd ahsa allah subhanah wteala khalqah klhm, waealam eddhm, fala yakhfaa ealayh 'ahad mnhm"
  19,95,"wswf yati kl fard min alkhalq rabih yawm alqiamat whdh, la mal lah wala wld meh"
  19,96,"'in aladhin amanuu biallah wattabaeu rusulah waeamiluu alsaalihat wafq shreh, sayajeal lahum alrhmn mahabatan wmwdt fi qulub ebadh"
  19,97,"f'inma yssarna hdha alquran bilisanik alearabii 'ayuha alrswl; litubashir bih almutaqin min atbaek, wtkhwwif bih almukadhibin shadiday alkhusumat balbatl"
  19,98,"wkthyrana 'ahlakna - 'ayuha alrasul - min al'umam alssabiqat qabl qwmk, ma taraa minhum ahdana wama tasmae lahum swtana, fkdhlk alkufaar min qwmk, nhlkhm kama 'ahlakna alssabiqin min qblhm. wafi hdha tahdid wweyd b'ihlak almukadhibin almeandyn"